1
00:02:07,360 --> 00:02:08,120
High God,

2
00:02:08,360 --> 00:02:09,600
do you still remember

3
00:02:09,960 --> 00:02:10,960
where I came from?

4
00:02:16,040 --> 00:02:16,880
Qingqiu.

5
00:02:17,840 --> 00:02:18,640
Exactly.

6
00:02:19,320 --> 00:02:21,579
Qingqiu is the sacred land of my fox clan.

7
00:02:21,640 --> 00:02:23,300
It is full of spiritual energy

8
00:02:23,440 --> 00:02:24,840
and protected by my clan.

9
00:02:25,800 --> 00:02:27,200
If you are willing to go there,

10
00:02:27,200 --> 00:02:29,800
though you can only be reincarnated as a demon,

11
00:02:29,840 --> 00:02:31,900
you can cultivate your magic earlier

12
00:02:32,320 --> 00:02:33,040
to seek

13
00:02:33,840 --> 00:02:35,240
what you are looking for.

14
00:02:35,600 --> 00:02:36,720
Human or demon,

15
00:02:36,840 --> 00:02:37,970
what does it matter?

16
00:02:38,640 --> 00:02:40,570
As long as it's in the mortal world,

17
00:02:41,560 --> 00:02:43,360
I don't care where my heart goes.

18
00:02:48,760 --> 00:02:50,680
This is the sacred artifact of the Qingqiu fox clan,

19
00:02:50,680 --> 00:02:51,640
the Soul-gathering Pearl.

20
00:02:51,640 --> 00:02:52,480
With it,

21
00:02:52,680 --> 00:02:53,400
you can definitely be reincarnated

22
00:02:53,400 --> 00:02:55,240
as a member of the Qingqiu fox clan.

23
00:02:55,240 --> 00:02:58,170
And it can quickly help you cultivate into human form

24
00:02:58,360 --> 00:02:58,960
and walk in

25
00:02:59,920 --> 00:03:00,920
the mortal world.

26
00:03:12,640 --> 00:03:13,440
Thank you.

27
00:04:39,680 --> 00:04:40,680
Hey, little girl.

28
00:04:42,040 --> 00:04:43,240
Are you calling me?

29
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:45,159
What's your name?

30
00:04:45,720 --> 00:04:46,960
I'm Yezi.

31
00:04:46,960 --> 00:04:47,600
And you?

32
00:04:48,080 --> 00:04:48,960
I'm Feilu.

33
00:04:50,040 --> 00:04:51,840
How long have you been locked up?

34
00:04:53,920 --> 00:04:55,180
About a month, I think.

35
00:04:55,360 --> 00:04:57,840
How did you get caught?

36
00:04:59,159 --> 00:05:00,680
I wasn't caught.

37
00:05:01,160 --> 00:05:02,320
You weren't caught?

38
00:05:02,520 --> 00:05:03,850
Then were you sent here?

39
00:05:05,280 --> 00:05:07,120
There was a famine in our village.

40
00:05:07,120 --> 00:05:08,960
The village chief sent me here

41
00:05:09,280 --> 00:05:11,800
as a sacrifice to Lady Tu.

42
00:05:12,120 --> 00:05:15,250
He hoped she would bless us with a good harvest next year.

43
00:05:15,480 --> 00:05:16,040
Bah!

44
00:05:16,040 --> 00:05:18,440
Isn't that total disregard for human life?

45
00:05:19,080 --> 00:05:20,340
I've accepted my fate.

46
00:05:21,800 --> 00:05:23,320
You've been locked up for a month.

47
00:05:23,320 --> 00:05:24,850
Why haven't they eaten you?

48
00:05:25,080 --> 00:05:26,560
They don't eat children.

49
00:05:26,960 --> 00:05:29,200
There used to be many children here.

50
00:05:29,320 --> 00:05:30,480
But they were all taken away

51
00:05:30,480 --> 00:05:32,000
to be made into medicine.

52
00:05:32,680 --> 00:05:35,120
I heard that to make the medicine,

53
00:05:35,120 --> 00:05:37,980
they need to calculate an auspicious date and time.

54
00:05:38,920 --> 00:05:41,400
I guess it's just not my turn yet.

55
00:05:41,560 --> 00:05:42,290
Don't worry.

56
00:05:42,760 --> 00:05:44,640
I'll definitely get you out of here.

57
00:05:44,640 --> 00:05:46,600
You can't even save yourself.

58
00:05:47,080 --> 00:05:48,140
How can you save me?

59
00:05:48,640 --> 00:05:49,159
I...

60
00:05:52,320 --> 00:05:53,850
My master is very powerful.

61
00:05:54,120 --> 00:05:55,600
He will definitely come and save me.

62
00:05:55,600 --> 00:05:57,120
Your master?

63
00:05:57,720 --> 00:05:59,520
How could he be more powerful than Lady Tu?

64
00:05:59,520 --> 00:06:00,400
In this world,

65
00:06:00,640 --> 00:06:02,600
there is no one more powerful than my master.

66
00:06:02,600 --> 00:06:04,720
Are you sure he will come?

67
00:06:09,520 --> 00:06:10,920
He will definitely come.

68
00:06:21,440 --> 00:06:22,080
Hyah!

69
00:06:24,320 --> 00:06:24,720
Hyah!

70
00:06:45,360 --> 00:06:46,120
We're here.

71
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:50,360
Let's go.

72
00:06:53,680 --> 00:06:54,540
Here they come.

73
00:06:59,520 --> 00:07:02,520
Prepare a welcome gift for our distinguished guests.

74
00:07:02,880 --> 00:07:03,680
Yes, yes.

75
00:07:22,480 --> 00:07:22,960
It seems

76
00:07:23,560 --> 00:07:25,290
they really think highly of us.

77
00:07:25,880 --> 00:07:27,000
We have to fight.

78
00:07:38,920 --> 00:07:40,080
Divine Taiji,

79
00:07:40,080 --> 00:07:40,920
manifestation of the universe,

80
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:41,720
thunder striking the purple skies,

81
00:07:41,720 --> 00:07:43,050
heavenly might strike.

82
00:07:43,920 --> 00:07:44,780
Zhen position.

83
00:08:21,400 --> 00:08:22,200
Good.

84
00:08:24,600 --> 00:08:26,460
As expected of a Golden Immortal.

85
00:08:26,480 --> 00:08:28,800
You can still fight so well without your immortal body.

86
00:08:28,800 --> 00:08:29,960
I'm impressed.

87
00:08:39,600 --> 00:08:40,440
It's Master.

88
00:08:40,799 --> 00:08:42,200
Master is here to save me.

89
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:52,530
If you encounter a monster,

90
00:08:52,800 --> 00:08:53,840
shout at this,

91
00:08:54,320 --> 00:08:55,380
'Sister, save me,'

92
00:08:55,400 --> 00:08:56,260
and I will come.

93
00:08:58,480 --> 00:08:59,840
Sister, save me.

94
00:09:04,040 --> 00:09:04,880
Crazy.

95
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:07,240
Save me, sister.

96
00:09:08,960 --> 00:09:09,760
It's Feilu.

97
00:09:12,120 --> 00:09:13,920
It's an avatar I gave him before.

98
00:09:14,160 --> 00:09:15,560
I've found his location.

99
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:16,680
Go save him.

100
00:09:17,200 --> 00:09:18,130
Leave this to us.

101
00:09:26,360 --> 00:09:28,020
Do you think I'm just for show?

102
00:09:35,160 --> 00:09:36,960
Treating me as a mere decoration

103
00:09:37,120 --> 00:09:39,380
wouldn't be very appropriate, would it?

104
00:09:40,720 --> 00:09:41,640
What a pain.

105
00:09:43,080 --> 00:09:43,880
Go.

106
00:10:04,160 --> 00:10:05,880
It was a lie after all.

107
00:10:14,360 --> 00:10:15,600
I'll just have to try.

108
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:48,120
I did it. I did it.

109
00:10:49,480 --> 00:10:50,640
Wow.

110
00:11:01,880 --> 00:11:02,610
Come with me.

111
00:11:03,240 --> 00:11:03,880
Let's go.

112
00:11:14,160 --> 00:11:14,760
Feilu.

113
00:11:14,760 --> 00:11:15,240
Shh.

114
00:11:22,800 --> 00:11:23,600
Shh.

115
00:12:04,840 --> 00:12:06,200
Wow.

116
00:12:09,720 --> 00:12:10,680
Brother Feilu,

117
00:12:10,680 --> 00:12:12,040
you are so amazing.

118
00:12:12,640 --> 00:12:13,770
I'm still learning.

119
00:12:18,080 --> 00:12:18,560
Yo,

120
00:12:19,160 --> 00:12:20,040
you two kids,

121
00:12:21,120 --> 00:12:22,720
where are you going?

122
00:13:30,360 --> 00:13:31,360
Pingjieqianghaihui.

123
00:13:31,320 --> 00:13:31,680
Pingjieqianghai.
